---
title: UML用例图-BL-20260626-01
tags: [UML 基线]
aliases: ["用例图-BL-20260626-01"]
---

@startuml
```plantuml
@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome

' ============================================
' 第一步：涉众 → Actor 映射
' ============================================
actor "库房人员" as WarehouseStaff
actor "财务人员" as FinanceStaff
actor "运维工程师" as MaintenanceEngineer
actor "招商业务员" as BusinessStaff
actor "库房主管" as WarehouseManager
actor "业务主管" as BusinessManager

' ============================================
' 第二步：从需求中提取用例
' ============================================
rectangle "设备管理" {
  ' --- 核心用例 ---
  usecase "常规出库" as UC_RegularOutbound
  usecase "紧急出库" as UC_EmergencyOutbound
  usecase "设备归还处理" as UC_ReturnHandling
  usecase "财务结算确认" as UC_FinancialSettlement
  usecase "紧急放行单审批" as UC_EmergencyReleaseApproval
  usecase "紧急备件领用" as UC_EmergencyPartsPickup
  usecase "紧急报修响应" as UC_EmergencyRepairResponse
  usecase "设备状态查询" as UC_DeviceStatusQuery

  ' --- 包含用例 ---
  usecase "核对设备型号与合同" as UC_VerifyModel
  usecase "执行出库检查" as UC_PerformChecklist

  ' --- 扩展用例 ---
  usecase "事后补录" as UC_PostRecording
  usecase "简化检查流程" as UC_SimplifiedCheck
}

' ============================================
' 第三步：建立关系
' ============================================

' Actor与用例关联
WarehouseStaff --> UC_RegularOutbound
WarehouseStaff --> UC_EmergencyOutbound
WarehouseStaff --> UC_ReturnHandling
WarehouseStaff --> UC_DeviceStatusQuery

FinanceStaff --> UC_FinancialSettlement
FinanceStaff --> UC_DeviceStatusQuery

MaintenanceEngineer --> UC_EmergencyPartsPickup
MaintenanceEngineer --> UC_EmergencyRepairResponse
MaintenanceEngineer --> UC_DeviceStatusQuery

BusinessStaff --> UC_EmergencyOutbound
BusinessStaff --> UC_DeviceStatusQuery

WarehouseManager --> UC_EmergencyReleaseApproval
BusinessManager --> UC_EmergencyReleaseApproval

' <<include>> 关系
UC_RegularOutbound ..> UC_VerifyModel : <<include>>
UC_RegularOutbound ..> UC_PerformChecklist : <<include>>
UC_EmergencyOutbound ..> UC_VerifyModel : <<include>>

' <<extend>> 关系
UC_EmergencyOutbound ..> UC_SimplifiedCheck : <<extend>>
UC_EmergencyPartsPickup ..> UC_PostRecording : <<extend>>

' ============================================
' 第四步：附加注解
' ============================================
note top of WarehouseStaff
  **Actor映射决策**
  库房人员：执行出库操作的核心角色
  财务人员：负责结算审核
  运维工程师：负责紧急维修和备件领用
  招商业务员：发起紧急出库申请
  库房主管/业务主管：审批紧急放行单
end note

note right of UC_RegularOutbound
  **用例合并理由**
  常规出库包含型号核对和检查清单执行，
  合并为一个完整业务流程
end note

note right of UC_EmergencyOutbound
  **用例拆分理由**
  紧急出库与常规出库业务流程不同，
  涉及审批和简化检查，故拆分为独立用例
end note

note right of UC_ReturnHandling
  **用例合并理由**
  设备归还后涉及库房和财务多个步骤，
  合并为统一的归还处理流程
end note

@enduml
```
@enduml